{"tid":1898944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好開心啊 有一萬蚊拎","createTime":"2020-02-26T10:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T10:09:06.000Z","uid":163207,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9c105bc0adea758a0859d16b7fff664905666c","tid":1898944,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:05:54.000Z","msg":"我屌晒你地老母 你地自己睇下個熱門似咩樣 成個熱門都係一萬蚊post 一睇就知啲公關公司同五毛又出離開膠post阻大家抗爭 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪已經無人記得依場運動 你地對唔對得住手足</span></span><br />\n我正式宣佈手足已成condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應承我 要用依一萬蚊去幫義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後補充一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b6dae2d65d2ab2a6f6e13ab120334470404e3c7","tid":1898944,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:06:40.000Z","msg":"最後補一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要多一萬"},{"pid":"40b56766488a100dbe6b38849c4fcb9c99b71b30","tid":1898944,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果呢個post都上唔到熱門，就證明場運動玩撚完，大家可以返屋企扑野啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"102e574d397a6297e55459ce69d1b8fe144dd8b4","tid":1898944,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"八月先填form，<br />\n<br />\n呢一年唔開心果陣只要諗起政府有一萬蚊派俾我，就開心翻晒<br />\n<br />\n打開銀包見到無錢果陣，只要諗起政府仲有一萬蚊未派俾我，我心中就富有起來。"}]}